                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Dont bother posting stuff about tradeskills if you do not want to start a rant fest, that is all I have to say about that.
<br />

<br />
As far as enchanter updates, it seems we are one of the classes that is played by only a few which makes it hard for us to get any changes or updates.  If they get thoughsands of feedbacks to change one thing and dozens of the other, SOE will look at the big number more (it might be better if they looked at both, but well we all know SOE).
<br />

<br />
Buff extensions will be great for us though, now all they have to do is fix a few spell bugs and we should be fine.  Im not finding we need more DPS, I would rather them lower some resists on specific spells, like mez or stun.  And I am currently useing no adept 3's or masters and I solo mobs 5 levels higher than me with out much problem, its all about knowing the timing of your spells and HOing like crazy.
<br />

<br />
On a side note:  Why did they slow down horses, I have no idea where that came from.  I mean Pally/SK mounts sure, but magic carpets I mean no one even has one yet....lol the mind boggles.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />______________________
